<p class="home-eyebrow">Interactive Computational Mathematics</p>

<h1 class="home-title">VisualMath</h1>

<p class="home-subtitle">
Explore numerical methods through fast, interactive, browser-based visualizations.
VisualMath turns abstract computational mathematics algorithms into dynamic, step-by-step apps.
</p>

